Class PartitionSettedRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.PartitionSettedRow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataGetters, InternalRow

    public class PartitionSettedRow
extends Object
implements InternalRow
    An implementation of InternalRow which provides a row the fixed partition value.

      • replaceRow

        public PartitionSettedRow replaceRow(InternalRow row)
        Replaces the underlying InternalRow backing this PartitionSettedRow.

        This method replaces the row data in place and does not return a new object. This is done for performance reasons.
